Michelin & Cie., (ML)  the worldâ€™s second-
largest tire maker, may expand in eastern  Europe ,  Ziarul
Financiar  reported today, citing Chief Executive Officer Michel
Rollier.  The French tiremaker is considering investing in Hungary,
Poland, Romania, Russia and Serbia and may open a plant in the
